✅ DO’s

Use a professional profile picture on LinkedIn.
Verify news before sharing it on WhatsApp.
Keep your private life separate from professional accounts.
Use Two-Factor Authentication (2FA) for security.
Share your academic achievements and projects.


❌ DON'Ts

Don't post confidential college or project data.
Don't engage in online arguments or "trolling."
Don't tag people in photos without their permission.
Don't share your location or travel plans in real-time.
Don't use offensive or unprofessional language.
